                <span style="font-size:20px;">
                 <span class="color_11">
                  The village of Cabo Pulmo was established in 1987 and currently has a population of 114,the National Marine Park of Cabo Pulmo was established in 1995 to protectthe oldestliving Coral Reef in North America. We welcome you to what is quickly becoming the biggest natural conservation success story in all of North America, Central America, Mexico &amp; Baja.
                 </span>
